## EX PARTE APPLICATION FOR ORDER SHORTENING TIME ON PLAINTIFF’S MOTION TO COMPEL DEFENDANT’S DEPOSITION; REQUEST TO SET CONDENSED BRIEFING SCHEDULE; SUPPORTING DECLARATION AND [PROPOSED] ORDER

**Ex Parte Hearing:**
